<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="P" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Patroness" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Patroness,</orth> protectress: <cit><quote>the p. of heavenly harmony,</quote> <bibl n="shak. shr 3.1.5" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. III, 1, 5</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>behold our p.</quote> <bibl n="shak. cor 5.5.1" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. V, 5, 1</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>Lucina, divinest p. to those that cry by night,</quote> <bibl n="shak. per 3.1.11" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. III, 1, 11</bibl></cit>.
